  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Direct Sales Rep",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Direct Sales Representative</strong></h2><p><strong>Roadshows • Events • Face-to-Face Engagement</strong></p><p>Enjoy active work, meeting new people, and learning skills you can actually use?<br />At Vision Organisation, you’ll be part of on-ground campaigns supporting brands at roadshows, pop-ups, and live events while building real-world communication and sales experience.</p><p>This is an <strong>entry-level, people-focused role</strong>.<br />No prior experience is required. Training is provided.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Engage members of the public at roadshows, pop-ups, and event booths</p></li><li><p>Represent client brands clearly, confidently, and professionally</p></li><li><p>Create positive customer interactions and meaningful conversations</p></li><li><p>Work with team members to support daily campaign goals</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Structured training and mentorship from day one</p></li><li><p>Performance-based growth with clear development pathways</p></li><li><p>Exposure to different campaigns and working locations</p></li><li><p>Supportive, team-oriented working environment</p></li><li><p>Performance-based incentives</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Who This Role May Suit</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Individuals at the start of their career or exploring sales and marketing</p></li><li><p>Those who enjoy interacting with people and staying active</p></li><li><p>Candidates open to learning, coaching, and feedback</p></li><li><p>Reliable individuals comfortable with on-ground, fast-paced work</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>If you’re interested in gaining hands-on experience in direct sales and public engagement, we’d be happy to connect.<br />📩 <strong>Apply via MyCareersFuture</strong><br />📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
